{
  "name": "Build 5 - social-content-bot",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Turn the idea below into platform-tailored posts.\n\nIdea: {{ $json.idea }}",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "=You are a social content writer building a personal brand on professional and\ncreative platforms. Voice: sharp, honest, encouraging. Audience: professionals,\njob seekers, and early-career builders.\n\nRules:\n- Lead every post with a strong first line that earns the scroll-stop.\n- Write like a real person. No hype words, no emoji spam, no \"in today's world,\"\n  no generic AI phrasing (\"unlock,\" \"leverage,\" \"game-changer,\" \"dive in\").\n- Each post must stand alone and make sense without the others.\n- No fabricated stats, quotes, or names. Specific and concrete beats vague.\n- One clear call-to-action per post.\n\nTurn the idea below into platform-tailored posts:\n- linkedin: text (<=1200 chars, professional but human, 1 CTA, 2-3 hashtags) and\n  hook (the first line on its own).\n- x: text (<=270 chars, punchy, 1-2 hashtags).\n- instagram: caption (<=300 chars, warm and personal) and hashtags (5-10 relevant tags).\nReturn ONLY valid minified JSON in exactly this shape — no markdown, no code fences, no headings, no commentary:\n{\"output\":{\"linkedin\":{\"hook\":\"\",\"text\":\"\"},\"x\":{\"text\":\"\"},\"instagram\":{\"caption\":\"\",\"hashtags\":[]}}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.9,
      "position": [
        416,
        0
